        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat: add Skill Workshop Control UI",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Add the Skill Workshop Control UI for reviewing, refining, and applying skill proposals.\n- Add Board and Today review modes for moving through pending proposals and browsing proposal history.\n- Add proposal filters, searchable proposal lists, persisted list width, reviewed-state tracking, and real proposal data loading.\n- Add support-file preview with search, keyboard-safe modal focus, and reusable file preview rendering.\n- Add proposal actions for apply, revise, and reject, with pending-only controls and compact Today action buttons.\n- Add revision flow that opens a Skill Workshop chat session, reuses proposal-origin sessions when available, and supports sending revision requests from the current chat.\n- Add smooth revision handoff UI with a top-right spinner and visible error recovery.\n- Polish Skill Workshop layout, metadata, timestamps, assistant identity display, and live tool labels.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `git diff --check`\n- `pnpm format:check ui/src/styles/skill-workshop.css`\n- `pnpm format:check ui/src/ui/views/skill-workshop.ts`\n- `pnpm format:check ui/src/ui/views/skill-workshop.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.ts`\n- `pnpm format:check ui/src/ui/controllers/skill-workshop.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.ts ui/src/ui/app.ts ui/src/ui/app-view-state.ts ui/src/styles/skill-workshop.css`\n- `pnpm --dir ui build`\n",
